msg":"前幾日預到差唔多情況，分享下解決方法<br />\n我個情況係本身板料太差，鏍絲位崩曬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LdE9zdK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLdE9zdK.jpg&h=9f4cccf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n度到本身係用3.5mm鋼牙鏍絲，可以用綠膠塞<br />\n度返D尺寸，用3D Printer印個定位器出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6UAHUfz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6UAHUfz.jpg&h=989604f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n定位鑽個8mm窿<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bbuhH9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbbuhH9e.jpg&h=97a88ed2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個窿邊搽上AB膠再塞入綠膠塞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q1VdguG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ1VdguG.jpg&h=ac49e2a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完～<br />\n<br />\nPS:<br />\n1. 本身一開始想用木棍做重建，不過手頭上冇<br />\n2. 定位器係用黎揾返原本鏍絲位嘅中心出黎，如果就咁鑽有機會咩埋一邊<br />\n3. 鏍絲換左再長少少嘅4mm鋼牙，令膠塞再逼實d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T03:35:28.000Z","msg":"唔好介意，<br />\n3d print果個step完全係多舊魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T03:37:28.000Z","msg":"我知，已經有Ching講左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c524a65f3e21a781d0cdb6f48003819fc990a6d","tid":2448413,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce47cb6de9e86777eab3317e7c77715de6469dc7","tid":2448413,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:33:59.000Z","msg":"用令梳開嫁 <br />\n<br />\n搵電線布膠度好厚度<br />\n<br />\n貼起鑽嘴到  開左邊位先<br />\n<br />\n再鑽機清晒中間d木 <br />\n<br />\n利申 木工 <br />\n<br />\n新手唔識既話應該搞唔到<br />\n<br />\n畫好尺寸起d木上邊先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T03:40:23.000Z","